    excerpt: "The Taskforce on Nature-related Financial Disclosures (TNFD) has joined TCFD on the global disclosure agenda. With biodiversity net gain now mandatory in the UK and being adopted across the EU, infrastructure developers and construction companies must rethink their relationship with natural ecosystems.",
